author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at how in the span of two weeks Apple has pulled it's cloud protections from the UK. This is a pretty massive blow to user privacy and while it seems bleak, i'll show you how to host a more safer cloud and down the road detach entirely from these companies. Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
title: Apple Removed Your Privacy From The Government...
